# ------------------
# Socrates inference
# ------------------
#
# Infer that Socrates is mortal.

@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>.
@prefix log: <http://www.w3.org/2000/10/swap/log#>.
@prefix : <http://example.org/ns#>.
@prefix skolem: <http://eyereasoner.github.io/.well-known/genid/d7882a29-44b8-4cbc-bc70-3bd11fba1fdb#>.

:Socrates a :Man.
:Man rdfs:subClassOf :Human.
:Human rdfs:subClassOf :Mortal.

(skolem:A skolem:B skolem:S) log:onNegativeSurface {
    skolem:A rdfs:subClassOf skolem:B.
    skolem:S a skolem:A.
    () log:onNegativeSurface {
        skolem:S a skolem:B.
    }.
}.

# query
(skolem:S skolem:C) log:onQuerySurface {
    skolem:S a skolem:C.
}.
